column5: Beautiful fish!!!  One Question? Where is everybody? You look like you had that place to yourself.   Clarence
Good going knightfisher Some nice specimens right there Thanks for sharing Leechman
Nice man, I'll be trying for the rainbows with a friend in a few weeks from now I hope.  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
Nice fish KF , but with a quick observation I surmise they were caught on possibly 4 different days ,Yes. Been way to slow down there this year compared to the last few.

Thanks guys. The fish were caught on different days. The last bow caught this past friday. The bite is off by at least 60%, making for some real tough fishing. Only a few of us dieharts are determined to get out there.
Living so close you're tempting me.  Nice fish.
yes, very nice fish and the parking lot is so handy compared to the Niagara River
Those are beauty fish!  Makes me miss living down there!
talk about teasing ....things are still froze over up here...lucky you!  nice shooting!!!!!!
